This repository is for various puppet modules and scripts.



---
Puppet Clean Stored Configs script

Requirements:
puppet with stored configs turned on
mysql backend
php, php-mysql module

Description:
This php script will remove all hosts, facts, and resources from the puppet mysql database that refer to a host that hasn't checked in with the puppet master in 7 (default) days.

Installation:
Copy the puppet-clean-stored-configs.php to your puppet master.  Execute "php puppet-clean-stored-configs.php".


